_+)$, then under additional conditions there is a\nthreshold for the birth of the impurity spectrum in the gap, that is\n$\\sigma(H_\\gamma)\\cap(\\lambda_-,\\,\\lambda_+)=\\emptyset$ for a small enough\n|\\gamma|.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 May 2015 15:39:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
